text: Kailua may refer to: ==Places in Hawaii== * Kailua, Honolulu County, Hawaii, a census-designated place on Hawaii's island of Oahu ** Kailua High School, in Honolulu county * Kailua-Kona, Hawaii, a census-designated place on Hawaii's island of Hawaii ** Kailua-Kona Airport, in Hawaii county ==Other uses== * USS Kailua (IX-71), formerly CS Dickenson, a civilian cable-laying ship that became an auxiliary ship of the United States Navy in the Second World War ==See also== * Kahlua (disambiguation)
title: Kailua (disambiguation)
